-- Надо ли нам наше маркетинговое воздействие распределять на все когорты поровну? Возможно, какие-то когорты более “щедрые” на покупку игровых предметов.

-- Средняя выручка на одного человека на один месяц для каждой когорты.

select *
		, extract('day' from ((select max(dtime_pay) from skygame.monetary) - month) / 30) as interval
		, avg_revenue_per_user/ (extract('day' from ((select max(dtime_pay) from skygame.monetary) - month) / 30)) as avg_revenue_per_month
from (
		select date_trunc('month', reg_date)::date as month
				, sum(cnt_buy*price) as revenue
				, count (distinct u.id_user) as cnt
				, sum(cnt_buy*price)/count (distinct m.id_user) as avg_revenue_per_user
		from skygame.monetary as m
			join skygame.users as u
				on m.id_user = u.id_user
			join skygame.log_prices as lp 
				on m.id_item_buy = lp.id_item
				and dtime_pay::date >= valid_from
				and dtime_pay::date < coalesce(valid_to, to_date('3000-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD'))
		where reg_date < (select max(dtime_pay) from skygame.monetary) - interval '1 month'
		group by month	
		order by month
	) as t1


